name: RegNet
description: Constructs a RegNet architecture from “Designing Network Design Spaces”.

properties._description:
model_name (string): Specific variant model of the RegNet model class, containing regnet_y_400mf, regnet_y_800mf... 
pretrained (bool): If True, returns a model pre-trained on ImageNet
progress (bool): If True, displays a progress bar of the download to stderr
num_classes (int): Number of categories
